data.title: Official Website
data.meta_description:
This is the official website of Afghanistan's first graffiti artist, Shamsia Hassani. Shamsia's works have been exhibited in USA, Afghanistan, India, Germany, Denmark, Switzerland, Italy, Turkey, and other countries. 
She has motivated hundreds of Afghans to bring in their creativity through her graffiti festivals, art classes, exhibitions in nine countries of three continents around the world.
